content: /*<![CDATA[*/ $('#title').html($('meta[name=map-description]').attr('content')); /*]]>*/ Zero Trust Secure Access Private Access Connector Version 2.37.0.2062 September 8, 2025—Zero Trust Secure Access Private Access Connector Version 2.37.0.2062 delivers key enhancements. Enhancements Adds resiliency to the IoT connection on the connector. Automates the recovery process by detecting IoT service issues and automatically reconnecting to restore normal operation.
